<HL>
   Technology &amp; Health:
   Digital Chip
   Is Endorsed
   By Microsoft
   ----
   By John R. Wilke
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
02/26/92
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B6
</SO>
